What you need to know:

Over the past week two of Dr Ruto’s most vocal supporters have dominated the news following searing attacks on President Kenyatta that descended to insults targeting his mother, former First Lady Mama Ngina Kenyatta.The harsh words, which also singled out the President’s powerful but reclusive younger brother Muhoho, were clear indicators of the anger and bitterness that prevails between the President and his estranged deputy.